{"tid":2381201,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"封區嘅背後原因係咩？","createTime":"2021-01-26T11:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T13:14:39.000Z","uid":143905,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"961bc14e9648c49f7c656cb3f2ce4bdaf1d5652c","tid":2381201,"uid":143905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"近排林鄭落order (收到order)要學支拿封區 想清零之外究竟想做啲咩呢 <br />\n<br />\n小弟總括咗兩大原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一 進行大規模洗腦<br />\n區域封鎖 入面嘅市民被限制自由 但與此同時 區外嘅人冇被限制 因此部分on9民眾（包括連登仔）就會覺得入面嘅人都有肺炎 因而支持政府封區 唔比佢哋周圍播毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 市民習慣咗你仲模式之後 就唔會再反對政府封區 同埋會自動乖乖地做港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 製造一個假象 武肺已under control<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUnder control完之後點？梗係拿拿林推行嗰個健康鹿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢鋪你班撚樣仲想搞革命都難啦 我保證完咗肺炎之後健康鹿一定會仲喺度 只不過會改個名 撚9我哋咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係諗到咁多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇高人知道個濕鳩林鄭仲想搞乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e1940b32646b40db855cb1aed692f88fc0b698","tid":2381201,"uid":126397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"想通關囉 廣東省同中共應該睇唔過眼香港搞咁耐都未好"},{"pid":"0398dd0e157a3838b9f93875f2035712d4b3d559","tid":2381201,"uid":368660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"温水煮蛙先,遲啲搞集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b949a8897b8bdcc7ab6b629319d914a8a339a70","tid":2381201,"uid":143905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e1940b32646b40db855cb1aed692f88fc0b698","tid"